{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576370/extras/lpgo2.png?t=1729269856\" /><br>REPLIKATOR is a top-down shooter <strong>with roguelike elements</strong>, set in an abandoned space science complex.<br>In the role of one of the mercenaries, you will have to fight against hordes of crazed robots and ectoplasmic monsters, while your boss calmly drinks beer in a safe compartment nearby. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576370/extras/short_11.08__online-video-cutter.com_.gif?t=1729269856\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dynamic battles. You will have to constantly move and aim well to survive!<br></li><li>Danger at every turn. Many different enemies and traps will not let you get bored.<br></li><li>Dozens of upgrade items. Explore stations looking for new upgrades for your character.<br></li><li>Meta progression. In this game, each death will only make you stronger, because after death you will be able to buy permanent improvements for your character and the hub ship.<br></li><li>Procedural generation! The location of rooms, enemies and traps, as well as weapons and all items are generated procedurally.<br></li><li>Space raccoon! and three more playable characters. All of them differ in starting characteristics, preferred weapons and special techniques.<br></li><li>Intriguing story. Explore the abandoned science complex and find out what happened here!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Rookie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576370/eb83e20933f4711a33d2bb0f5f6ae6fd14be121d.jpg"},{"name":"This is the norm here","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576370/62c0006166812cd1a4678d1d74a903b1299ed484.jpg"},{"name":"Not a bad start","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1576370/b3bdcdc4ceef7b